H0.text: The Hubble sequence that classifies galaxies is also known for being drawn in what shape. Spiral

H1.text: The Hubble sequence that classifies galaxies is also known for being drawn in what shape. Circle

H2.text: The Hubble sequence that classifies galaxies is also known for being drawn in what shape. Ellipse

H3.text: The Hubble sequence that classifies galaxies is also known for being drawn in what shape. Tuning-fork

A4.text: The Hubble sequence is often colloquially known as the Hubble tuning-fork diagram because the shape in which it is traditionally represented resembles a tuning fork.
